body:
### In this texture pack, all MineShield players became mobs. What will become this or that MineShield player depended on the associations of streamers, their chat and mine including. This mod replaced 32 mobs and one item. I wanted to say a special thanks to Sec_B and ThePolClassic for their help and support.
 ---
### Change List:
- ***CapXenomorph*** - glowing squid;
- ***Faradey*** - fox;
- ***Alfedov*** - snow golem;
- ***Arlabus*** - evoker;
- ***Diamkey*** - zombie;
- ***Alcest_M*** - turtle;
- ***Venazar*** - zombified piglin;
- ***_Evgexa_*** - skeleton;
- ***_DEB_*** - parrot;
- ***_HeO_*** - iron golem;
- ***Dushenka*** - sheep;
- ***Jay_Pokerman*** - witch;
- ***KrolikMun*** - rabbit;
- ***Just_s*** - sniffer;
- ***ObsidianTime69*** - pig + sounds;
- ***_PWGood_*** - shulker + sounds;
- ***NikiWright***- panda;
- ***Sec_B*** - polar bear;
- ***Santos*** - squid;
